Package: pamir-ai-eink-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         device-tree-compiler
Recommends: pamir-ai-eink-tests,
            linux-headers-vendor-rk35xx | linux-headers-current-rk35xx | linux-headers-edge-rk35xx | raspberrypi-kernel-headers
Description: Pamir AI E-Ink Display Driver (DKMS)
 This package provides a DKMS (Dynamic Kernel Module Support) driver
 for Pamir AI E-Ink displays using the SSD1680 controller.
 .
 Supported platforms:
  - Raspberry Pi CM5 (BCM2712)
  - Rockchip RK3566 (Radxa Zero 3/3W)
  - Rockchip RK3576 (ArmSom CM5 IO)
 .

Package: pamir-ai-eink-tests
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         build-essential,
         python3,
         python3-pil,
         python3-requests
Description: Test programs for Pamir AI E-Ink Display Driver
 This package provides test programs and examples for the Pamir AI
 E-Ink display driver.
